	   <tr><td colspan=2>In the course of my reading and preparing to purchase and then play Everquest, I am confused with the trade skills.<br><br>What part do they play in the game?' I have ordered instructions book, not arrived as yet<br><br>If you do some trade, can you do it over and over to get to the level desirable?&quot;<br><br>Is any trade skill more desirable than the other?&quot;<br><br>Having been a Bricklayer for 35 years, I might have a leg up in the real world, but Alas! I seek to enter your world and I await your instructions and superior knowledge, Hail! All Fishers, Clay, and other skills<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Mon Dec 17 20:09:43 2001</em><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
