	   <tr><td colspan=2>Trades skill will also be used in doing the coldain prayer shawl quests.  From my experiance start your trade skills early in life and wont be as much of a pain to do when you get to be high lvl to do the shawl quests. The shawl quests IMHO are really nice for casters such as druids. The final product that you make is +7 wis and int  also gives an effect of a high lvl chnater mana regen spell which means lower downtime.  I got to get back to work good luck all.  I hope I gave you some help in the trade skill dept.<br>&nbsp;<br>Jensen Greatwar<br>46 human druid of brell serilis.<br>Proud member of Death Stalker Elite Guard</td></tr>
